  "description": "You create a twisting pattern of colors in a 30-foot Cube within range. The pattern appears for a moment and vanishes. Each creature in the area who can see the pattern must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or have the &amp;Reference[charmed apply=false] condition for the duration. While Charmed, the creature has the &amp;Reference[incapacitated apply=false] condition and a Speed of 0.\n\nThe spell ends for an affected creature if it takes any damage or if someone else uses an action to shake the creature out of its stupor.",
